column1: Daily Weather Observations for Condobolin, New South Wales for October 2021
Prepared at 05:36 UTC on Tuesday 26 October 2021   IDCJDW2032.202110
Most observations from Condobolin Airport, but some from Condobolin Agricultural Research Station.
Temperature, humidity, wind, pressure and rainfall observations are from Condobolin Airport AWS {station 050137}
Cloud and evaporation observations are from Condobolin Ag Research Stn {station 050052}
